  "observations": [
    "Self-referential page tree (Page.parentPageId) with drag-to-reparent — single hierarchical primary navigation",
    "Block is polymorphic entity with discriminator field 'type' and 15+ variants (paragraph/heading/list/toggle/table/database/embed/code/callout/quote/divider/image/video/file/ai)",
    "Slash-command (/) menu inserts blocks contextually at caret — inline creator surface",
    "Markdown-style inline shortcuts auto-convert on space (## → heading, [] → todo, --- → divider)",
    "Database is a Block whose payload is a multi-view collection (table/board/gallery/calendar/timeline/list) — same rows, different DatabaseView projections",
    "Row-as-page duality: clicking a row opens it as a full Page detail with hero header + property panel",
    "Property kinds form runtime-builder schema (text/number/select/multi-select/date/person/file/checkbox/url/email/phone/formula/relation/rollup/created_time/last_edited)",
    "Conditional visibility via formula-driven Property.visibilityFormula expression",
    "Linked databases project the same source rows under a different view (mirror projection, no copy)",
    "Permission inheritance chain: PagePermission resolves through parent Page → Workspace, with explicit override badge when broken",
    "Invitation lifecycle is separate entity with token + expiresAt + accepted/revoked states",
    "Ephemeral PresenceSession overlay (avatars + cursors) is non-persistent, derived from active connections",
    "Comments anchor to either Block or text range within a Block (multi-anchor) and form threads with resolve toggle",
    "Typed mentions (@person, [[Page]], +database) auto-create Mention entities and produce backlinks on target",
    "AI-generated content kept as separate AiGeneration record with regenerate-from lineage and accept-into-block transition",
    "Template entity with scope tier (personal/workspace/marketplace) — installer pattern with category facets",
    "Indent/outdent (Tab/Shift-Tab) reparents block under previous sibling — keyboard tree-builder",
    "Inline-editable hero header with title, icon, cover — atomic detail-archetype heading",
    "Quick-find (Cmd+P) palette with typed filter chips (type:/in:/by:) — global-command-palette",
    "Page version history rail with append-only snapshots; restore creates new version, never mutates past",
    "Soft-delete: archived flag with 30-day grace before hard-delete; restore is non-destructive replace",
    "RBAC × resource permission matrix at workspace level (role × capability grid)",
    "Publish-with-subtree checklist controls which child pages are exposed in public site",
    "Sparse-FK Comment (pageId XOR blockId) — anchor target determined by which FK is set",
    "Dual-mode search: simple typed-syntax bar and structured advanced filter — two projections of same query entity"
  ]
}